'''1960年NBA選秀'''（1960 NBA draft）是[[國家籃球協會|國家籃球協會]]（NBA）的第十四次年度選秀。本次選秀於1960年4月11日舉行，8支NBA球隊輪流從美國大學籃球業餘運動員中挑選新隊員。在每一輪選秀中，各隊按照前一賽季（1959-60賽季）的勝負成績逆序選擇。[[明尼亞波利斯湖人|明尼亞波利斯湖人]]也有參加本次選秀，但在開季前遷移主場至[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]變成[[洛杉磯湖人|洛杉磯湖人]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/lakers/history/lakers_history_new.html|title=History of the Lakers|work=NBA.com/Lakers|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|date=|accessdate=2010-01-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100107202448/http://www.nba.com/lakers/history/lakers_history_new.html|archivedate=2010-01-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>。此次選秀共選了21輪，總計選進100位球員。

==選秀情況==
來自[[辛辛那提大學|辛辛那提大學]]的[[奧斯卡·羅伯森|奧斯卡·羅伯森]]被[[辛辛那提皇家|辛辛那提皇家]]以地緣選秀的方式選中。但因為皇家隊同時握有狀元籤，所以同樣視為選秀狀元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/players/robertson_bio.html|title=Oscar Robertson Bio|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|date=|accessdate=2009-09-10|archive-date=2011-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110303202754/http://www.nba.com/history/players/robertson_bio.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2000/06/29/sports/pro-basketball-clippers-go-to-high-school-to-get-miles.html|title=Clippers Go to High School to Get Miles|work=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|date=2000-06-29|accessdate=2009-09-10|first=Mike|last=Wise|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204332/http://www.nytimes.com/2000/06/29/sports/pro-basketball-clippers-go-to-high-school-to-get-miles.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最終在菜鳥年就奪下[[NBA年度最佳新秀|年度最佳新秀]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/awards_rookieofyear.html|title=Rookie of the Year|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|date=|accessdate=2009-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100329231204/http://www.nba.com/history/awards_rookieofyear.html|archive-date=2010-03-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。來自[[西維吉尼亞大學|西維吉尼亞大學]]的[[傑瑞·威斯特|傑瑞·威斯特]]在第2順位被[[明尼亞波利斯湖人|明尼亞波利斯湖人]]選中。
本屆的三位新秀羅伯森、威斯特以及第6順位的[[兰尼·威尔肯斯|兰尼·威尔肯斯]]最終被選進[[奈史密斯籃球名人紀念堂|名人堂]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/awards/hof.html|title=Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame Inductees|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|date=|accessdate=2009-10-28|archive-date=2010-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101225151844/http://www.basketball-reference.com/awards/hof.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他們三位之後也都被選為[[NBA50大巨星|NBA50大巨星]]一列<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/50greatest.html|title=The NBA's 50 Greatest Players|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-06-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100613002013/http://www.nba.com/history/50greatest.html|archivedate=2010-06-13|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

羅伯森的成就包括在[[1970-71_NBA賽季|1971年]]於[[密爾瓦基公鹿|密爾瓦基公鹿隊]]得到1次[[NBA總冠軍列表|NBA總冠軍]]、[[1963-64_NBA賽季|1964年]]得到[[NBA最有價值球員|最有價值球員]]、11次以及12次{{link-en|明星賽資格|List of NBA All-Stars}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/players/robertson_bio.html|title=Oscar Robertson Bio|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-06-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100623121156/http://www.nba.com/history/players/robertson_bio.html|archivedate=2010-06-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>威斯特在湖人隊打了14個球季，成就包括於[[1971-72_NBA賽季|1972年]]贏得總冠軍、12次[[NBA最佳陣容|NBA最佳陣容]]以及14次明星賽資格<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/players/west_bio.html|title=Jerry West Bio|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-06-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100623150123/http://www.nba.com/history/players/west_bio.html|archivedate=2010-06-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>，他之後在湖人隊執教了3個球季<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/westje01c.html|title=Jerry West Coaching Record|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-06-12|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125222805/https://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/westje01c.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。威尔肯斯的成就包括9次明星賽資格。在退休之後他成為一位成功的總教練，並於[[1978-79_NBA賽季|1979年]]執教[[西雅圖超音速|西雅圖超音速]]贏得總冠軍，之後在[[1993-94_NBA賽季|1994年]]獲得[[NBA年度最佳教練|年度最佳教練]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/players/wilkens_bio.html|title=Lenny Wilkens Coaching Record|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-06-12|archive-date=2016-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503065911/http://www.nba.com/history/players/wilkens_bio.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。並擁有執教最多場次比賽的紀錄（2,487場比賽）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/NBA_stats.html|title=NBA Coach Register|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-06-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100615054146/http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/NBA_stats.html|archivedate=2010-06-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>，而在1998年以教練的身份進入[[奈史密斯籃球名人紀念堂|名人堂]]，成為在[[John_Wooden|John Wooden]]及[[比尔·沙尔曼|比尔·沙尔曼]]之後，第3位同時擁有球員及教練的身份入選名人堂的球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/news/story?id=1879063|title=Sharman among those enshrined in Basketball Hall of Fame|date=2004-09-10|work=ESPN.com|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|accessdate=2010-06-12|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006070049/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/news/story?id=1879063|dead-url=no}}</ref>第3順位的[[達雷爾·伊姆霍夫|達雷爾·伊姆霍夫]]與第5順位的[[Lee_Shaffer|Lee Shaffer]]都打過明星賽<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/i/imhofda01.html|title=Darrall Imhoff Statistics|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-06-12|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129225723/https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/i/imhofda01.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/s/shaffle01.html|title=Lee Shaffer Statistics|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|date=|accessdate=2010-06-12|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111183926/https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/s/shaffle01.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第8順位的[[薩奇·桑德斯|薩奇·桑德斯]]生涯共在[[波士頓塞爾提克|波士頓塞爾提克]]贏得8座NBA冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/s/sandeto01.html|title=Tom Sanders Statistics|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|date=|accessdate=2010-06-12|archive-date=2012-10-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B7D7KISx?url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/s/sandeto01.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，退休後曾於1978年短暫執教塞爾提克隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/sandeto01c.html|title=Tom Sanders Coaching Record|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|date=|accessdate=2010-06-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100523012532/http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/sandeto01c.html|archivedate=2010-05-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>。第39順位的[[Al_Attles|Al Attles]]也擁有成功的教練生涯，執教[[金州勇士|舊金山/金州勇士]]14個球季，並在[[1974-75_NBA賽季|1975年]]贏得總冠軍，球衣號碼16號也被勇士隊退休<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/attleal01c.html|title=Al Attles Coaching Record|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|date=|accessdate=2010-06-12|archive-date=2012-09-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Agmxs7hR?url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/attleal01c.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

